              },
              "free_text": [
                " methodology for",
                "  reaction-rate."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "calculation.",
                "The reaction-rate has been estimated, using the",
                "methodology developed by Jassby and Towner.",
                "      ***  ***  ***  ***  ***  ***  ***  ***",
                "in some cases, when cross-section information is not",
                "available, the authors have assumed a functional",
                "dependence of the form",
                "   (sig) = (a/E)exp(g(E)),",
                "where g(E) accounts for barrier penetration of only the",
                "lithium target.",
                " And all cross sections were assumed to be flat above",
                "highest measured energy.",
                "      ***  ***  ***  ***  ***  ***  ***  ***",
                ".considered 3 reactions are",
                "  H-1  +  Li-6   beam-target reactions.",
                "  H-1  +  Li-6   thermo-nuclear reaction, and",
                "  Li-6 +  Li-6   thermo-nuclear reaction.",
                " H+ ions are assumed to have isotropic velocity",
                " distribution."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " estimated error of 20 percent,",
                "results from uncertainties:",
                "  * in the cross sections,",
                "  * in extrapolation of cross sect. to higher energy,",
                "and in calculational approximation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "below the ion-temperature of 80 keV,",
                " Li-6 + Li-6 reactions are less than that for H-1 +Li-6",
                " by a factor of at least 10**3, and",
                "with rising temperature, this factor decreases and at",
                "270 keV, it becomes about 10."
              ]
            }
          ],
